<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/597664-is-this-the-best-tom-robbins-book-to-start">Is this the best Tom Robbins book to start with? - I haven&#39;t read any of his work yet...</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_597664'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8682.Jitterbug_Perfume">like</a></span>

